    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "The Spy Who Shoved Me",
        "Description": "A recording between megalomaniac Augusto Albarez and compromised Agent Felix Albert was found washed up on shore:\r\r-\r\r&quot;I, THE Augusto Albarez, plan on making land SO unhabitable that everyone will have to adapt to my all-new watery city!&quot;\r\r&quot;. . . Do you always stand close to edges and cliffs when you expuld your monologue?&quot;\r\r&quot;Well, if I&apos;m not ready to dive in at any moment, who will?&quot;\r\r&quot;Fair enough. Let&apos;s go swimming, Albarez.&quot;\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as Ashley.",
